### 1. GET published events sorted by startDate

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=status eq 'Published' && orderby=startDate

### 2. GET events filtered by type 'Workshop'

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=eventType eq 'Workshop'

### 3. GET all registrations for a specific event

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Registrations?$filter=event_ID eq '8d4b9230-9dad-11d1-80b4-00c04fd430c8'

### 4. POST a new registration

POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "event_ID": "8d4b9230-9dad-11d1-80b4-00c04fd430c8",
    "attendeeName": "Jane Smith",
    "attendeeEmail": "jane@example.com",
    "ticketType": "General",
    "amountPaid": 50.00
}

### 5. GET speakers sorted by rating desc

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Speakers?$orderby=rating desc

### 6. GET events with available seats

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=registeredCount lt maxAttendees

### 7. PATCH event status to 'Published'

PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events('8d4b9230-9dad-11d1-80b4-00c04fd430c8')
Content-Type: application/json

{"status": "Published"}

### 8. POST feedback

POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "event_ID": "8d4b9230-9dad-11d1-80b4-00c04fd430c8",
    "attendeeEmail": "jane@example.com",
    "overallRating": 5
}
 